songs.title: Tik Tok/Push It
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: All & Leigh-Anne & Jesy]
Wake up in the morning feeling like P-Diddy
Grab my glasses, I'm out the door I'm gonna
Hit the city
Before I leave brush my teeth with a bottle of Jack
Cause when I leave for the night I ain't coming back

[Pre-Chorus: Leigh-Anne & All & Perrie]
I'm talking pedicure on our Toes toes
Trying on all our Clothes clothes
Boys ringing up our Phones phones
Yeah, drop top and playing our favourite  CD's
Pulling up to the Party
Tryna get a little bit Tipsy

[Chorus: All]
Don't stop, make it pop, DJ, blow my speakers up
Tonight, I'mma fight 'til we see the sunlight
Tik tok, on the clock, but the party don't stop no
Oh oh oh, oh oh oh
Push it, ah push it
Push it real good
Oh baby baby, baby
Oh baby baby, baby

[Bridge: Jade & Leigh-Anne & Jesy & (All)]
You build me up, you break me down
My heart, it pounds, yeah, you got me
Put your hands up, put your hands up, put your hands up yeah
(Now, the party don't start 'til we walk in)

[Chorus: All]
Don't stop, make it pop, DJ, blow my speakers up
Tonight, I'mma fight 'til we see the sunlight
Tik tok, on the clock, but the party don't stop no
Oh oh oh, oh oh oh
Push it, ah push it
Push it real good, oh
